strategies: I didn't use ant strategies; I just made sure to focus and pay attention
familiar: It was cities that I have heard of or even been in
memorable: Cities that I've heard of but are also popular
unique: Cities that I haven't heard of or that I've heard of but as far as I know don't exist in more than one state/country
realistic: Cities that I know of. Some I didn't know and just didn't sound like real city names to me so I rated them less realistic.
